Inline math: the Pythagorean theorem says $a^2 + b^2 = c^2$.

Display math:

$$
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} e^{-x^2} , dx = \sqrt{\pi}
$$

A matrix:

$$
A = \begin{pmatrix} 1 & 2 \ 3 & 4 \end{pmatrix}
$$

